FBIS4-29043 "dreas115_a_94008" FBIS-EAS-94-115 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Tokyo Receives Draft of UN Sanctions From U.S. Tokyo Receives Draft of UN Sanctions From U.S. OW1506125894 Tokyo KYODO in English 1250 GMT 15 Jun 94 OW1506125894 Tokyo KYODO English BFN [Text] Tokyo, June 15 KYODO -- Japan has received a draft resolution the United States plans to submit to the UN Security council to impose sanctions on North Korea for its suspected nuclear arms development program, a chief government spokesman said Wednesday. The proposed sanctions "are in no way easygoing," Chief Cabinet Secretary Hiroshi Kumagai said without elaboration.
